snippet.textDisplay: I am an Indian. First of all, love and more love to all Pakistanis. Being an atheist it's hard to like this song. But such creation dedicated to God makes one think how beautiful worshipping is and can be without even needing to be violent. Such songs teach us Allah wants us to love each other. He could never ask us to kill one another. He says love each other, help everyone around you. This world is all yours to embrace, to live as one.
